1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:02,000
Night owls: this one
change makes mornings bearable.

2
00:00:02,000 --> 00:00:08,000
If you're a night owl, mornings feel like
torture. No amount of motivation fixes it.

3
00:00:08,000 --> 00:00:18,000
But here's the thing: your chronotype is partly flexible. You can't become
a morning person overnight. But you CAN shift 30 minutes per week.

4
00:00:18,000 --> 00:00:24,000
Set your wake time 15 minutes earlier this week. Add
morning light. In 4 weeks that's a full hour shift.

5
00:00:24,000 --> 00:00:28,000
I built an app that coaches
you through this. Free. 30 seconds.

